{"tid":982642,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"老老竇竇tvb寫節目表啲員工都幾屈機","createTime":"2019-01-15T09:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T10:33:46.000Z","uid":92376,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"846cbbc0295315337e3d46e5644626116cd12d67","tid":982642,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T09:30:22.000Z","msg":"牛仔隊用長網接球時太過心急，捕球顯得有點吃力，情況告急，仁慈的王子給予額外的入球獎賞，牛仔隊能否把握這黃金機會？迷彩隊兩位女將捕球時顯得有板有眼，在短短一分鐘內已成功捕捉4個入球，及後在豆袋九宮格環節亦攻防兼顧，有勇有謀，令牛仔隊受壓作賽！進入「終極對決」的推車比賽，牛仔隊未能靠大車之助突破分數，迷彩隊在Regina姐姐指導下，如願以償地以手中大車將障礙車撞入得分區，但賽果難料&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n可以將兒童節目內容寫到高潮迭起緊張刺激兼而有之 果種功力唔係講笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02fec6ee09bd6eb7f747d807de20d85029a12a6","tid":982642,"uid":65371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T09:31:21.000Z","msg":"乜鳩嘢節目表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9f06888c172c438a42e9d5b8546cfb1ae8980d4","tid":982642,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b02fec6ee09bd6eb7f747d807de20d85029a12a6","tid":982642,"uid":65371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T09:31:21.000Z","msg":"乜鳩嘢節目表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T09:31:48.000Z","msg":"官網節目表copy出黎架"},{"pid":"21ee0ffbc3c7bc869e4ef37f17ce6b2c83a324dc","tid":982642,"uid":33539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T09:32:13.000Z","msg":"怎料"},{"pid":"672e7e96f5b1aabb272b1f1c4bd9c980fc64dfdb","tid":982642,"uid":16743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T10:33:46.000Z","msg":"PR寫的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}